Naga Chaitanya Akkineni -LRB- born 23 November 1986 -RRB- is an Indian film actor who works in Telugu cinema .
He debuted in the 2009 film Josh , directed by newcomer Vasu Varma and produced by Dil Raju .
Prior to the release of his first film , he signed his second film with Indira Productions , which was to be directed by Gautham Menon .
Ye Maaya Chesave released in February 2010 with comparisons drawn to his father Akkineni Nagarjuna 's romantic film , Geethanjali .
His next movie was Sukumar 's 100 % Love co-starring Tamannaah .
The movie was shortly followed by Dhada and Bejawada .
Chaitanya also appeared in the movie Autonagar Surya .
In 2013 , he appeared in Thadaka .
The film Manam also featured other members of his family .
He has also appeared in Oka Laila Kosam .